![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1631746886463-YFGZQAM42X4A9SKV4NGD/195.jpg?format=original)

This week on the podcast we tackle Descender from the Image Comics universe! Descender follows one young robot’s struggle to stay alive in a universe where androids have been outlawed and bounty hunters lurk on every planet. It's a cosmic odyssey from the brilliant mind of Jeff Lemire. What does it have to say about humanity, fear, and war? Are robots meant to be our equals? Why is Driller such a killer? Find out the answers to SOME of these questions in this super Sci-Fi edition of the Major Issues Podcast

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
